title: Easy Almond-Crusted Salmon with Herby Veggies & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Set the table and get ready to impress with this succulent salmon dish. It’s impressive enough for a special occasion and easy
enough for a weeknight dinner. The crust is so delicious that we reckon you’ll be eating the loose bits straight off the tray. You can thank us later!

